AmSafe, Inc. Wins Federal Contract Valued at Up to $4,780,549.86
Feb 28 16
AmSafe, Inc. won a federal contract valued at up to $4,780,549.86 from the Defense Logistics Agency, Columbus, Ohio, for gunner restraint kits.


